dct_title_s: Sketch of the public surveys in the state of Minnesota
dct_description_sm: Cartographic Details: Scale 1:1,040,480. "St. Paul, October 19th, 1863." Above neat line at right: "Ho. Reps. ex. doc. no. 1, 38th Cong., 1st sess." Shows surveyed area of Minnesota. Endorsed by Surveyor General W.D. Washburn. Dimensions: 58 x 51 centimeters
